modules.description: Converts between pipes of Cstruct.t and strings or Bigsubstrings, enabling efficient data transformation and streaming. Works directly with Async.Pipe readers and writers for Cstruct.t, string, and Bigsubstring types. Useful for network or file I/O where data needs to be processed in different memory representations without unnecessary copying.

This module directly converts between `Cstruct.t` and `Core.Bigsubstring.t`, enabling efficient data manipulation without unnecessary copying. It provides functions for reading from and writing to Async IO handles using `Cstruct.t`, facilitating low-level network or file operations that require precise memory control. The `Pipe` submodule bridges Async pipes between `Cstruct.t`, strings, and `Bigsubstring.t`, supporting streaming data transformations in memory-bound contexts.
